{"word":"πιάζω","slug":"πιάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πιάζω</el></b> [Doric form of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πιέζω\">πιέζω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘take firm hold of’, <b>grasp,</b> by the hand <b><a href='B:510 3:7'>Ac 3:7</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘take under control’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a>, <b>seize, arrest <a href='B:500 7:30'>J 7:30</a>, <a href='B:500 7:32'>32</a>, <a href='B:500 7:44'>44</a>; <a href='B:500 8:20'>8:20</a>; <a href='B:500 10:39'>10:39</a>; <a href='B:500 11:57'>11:57</a>; <a href='B:510 12:4'>Ac 12:4</a>; <a href='B:540 11:32'>2 Cor 11:32</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of animals, <b>catch <a href='B:500 21:3'>J 21:3</a>, <a href='B:500 21:10'>10</a>; <a href='B:730 19:20'>Rv 19:20</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πῆχυς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πίε\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}